data.description: Rare opportunity to get into this awesome 3 bedroom 2.5 bath townhouse at a great price! Beautifully decorated with neutral walls; updated kitchen and SS appliances, wood laminate flooring throughout,. Walk onto your enclosed screened in porch or access even more space to entertain or barbeque with the family on the fenced in courtyard that overlooks a park and a lake. Roof installed 2023; AC 2023, Water heater 2021. This is a terrific starter home or great for anyone downsizing. Take advantage of this great buy!
